h=101a6e7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/臺灣對東日本大震災之援助及各界反應</a><br />\n<br />\n中央政府、各地方政府、主要政黨、企業界、影視圈、慈善與宗教等民間團體亦踴躍響應捐助金錢物資，並親赴災區賑濟和協助短中長期重建。依參與之廣、時間之久、金額之高，此次對「東日本大震災」之援助堪稱臺灣史上最大規模的國民外交。中華民國政府與台灣人民捐助至少日圓200億元（外交部報告數字為新臺幣68.4億，因捐助管道有別且各時期匯率差異而有66至73億元等不同估算），居世界第一，且超過有捐款的其他93個國家總額。由台灣寄出的救援物資保守估計亦超過上千公噸。日本政府及日本傳播媒體對此向台灣表達感謝之意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bdp-taiwan.blogspot.hk/2014/06/1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbdp-taiwan.blogspot.hk%2F2014%2F06%2F1.html&d=hf9CeJIU7mZVUXy84RxF7W6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=917d06aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://bdp-taiwan.blogspot.hk/2014/06/1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n［李登輝・特別寄稿］日台の絆は永遠に〔１〕"},{"pid":"42b0af014098e7b9dbfe77b79b1920624aa20d70","tid":547650,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f095609f565bf4da76200661ec1df228b7c409","tid":547650,"uid":138502,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3bcdfed7273732828c4415e415b2b2a1095e4aad","tid":547650,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T16:39:35.000Z","msg":"達賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:26:06.000Z","msg":"呢個達賴同以前其他達賴好唔同 識玩政治講野有文有路又有哲理 真正「智慧深似海」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜人始終會死 之後西藏就會失去精神領袖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f86797f4a2140c128f82ce50bea586dac4dcfc6","tid":547650,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"47f095609f565bf4da76200661ec1df228b7c409","tid":547650,"uid":138502,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3bcdfed7273732828c4415e415b2b2a1095e4aad","tid":547650,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T16:39:35.000Z","msg":"達賴<img 