br />\n<br />\n做歌影視<br />\n成功ge話好易會紅到個明星出黎<br />\n如果唔係好難深入人心<br />\n而只要個明星一叛變<br />\n之前係背後ge工作就白廢晒<br />\n而令1個人叛變係好易ge事...<br />\n<br />\n至於點包裝件事...就睇你啦...<br />\n我冇咁大本事指教人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680729899dec0f8369ee9ec69ecaae6ae4b2b46e","tid":547650,"uid":12633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:26:28.000Z","msg":"文化救港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請支持香港文化"},{"pid":"029982152d57a207994cf96480af8462e25fde55","tid":547650,"uid":16676,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:36:30.000Z","msg":"如果唔係教授, 三子<br />\n咁傳媒做訪問有關香港民主既應該搵邊個, 邊個敢發聲<br />\n<br />\n各界組織動員, 推動力量唔通係今日既高登同連登?<br />\n學聯而家一片散沙, 其他兩位教授都閃左<br />\n白鴿黨已經收皮<br />\n<br />\n三子加教授起碼將民主運動推到另一個地方<br />\n唔再係白鴿黨出頭先丫<br />\n<br />\n所以我係肯定佢既力量同應受尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfaf66d53bc1b7d9aa463b0204e7ef5595652ff2","tid":547650,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T02:29:49.000Z","msg":"用YouTube推廣香港啦<br />\n<br />\n例子 結他高手YouTubers<br />\n<br />\n俄佬 Igor<br />\n泡菜 Yenne Lee, Andrew Foy, <br />\nJungha Sung<br />\n<br />\n巴西 Luciana Zogbi<br />\n瑞典 Gabriella<br />\n印尼 Joey Alexander the kid jazz pianist<br />\n<br />\n你哋班90後00後<br />\n畀你個虎媽 迫彈琴學音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一生一體藝咁樣<br />\n<br />\n所以香港實有唔少 音樂高手嘅 <br />\n諗諗佢"},{"pid":"4c3dd23385932398ed5166afb95b1990023e0833","tid":547650,"uid":75139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36c8b6c7786645fab034f50a93a58e7a3b94f0ab","tid":547650,"uid":13724,"like":43,"dislike":6,"score":37,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T15:59:30.000Z","msg":"雙學3子攞到和平獎嘅話可唔可以將香港推到西藏地位<img src=\"/assets